Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（改编自艾萨克阿西莫夫的小说）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候 我告诉母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I was a child, I told my mother
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.63,0:01:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想了解银河帝国里的每一颗行星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to learn every planet in the Galactic Empire…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从中心开始向外延伸 直到星之尽头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}beginning in the center and moving out to Star's End.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天晚上她都给我讲故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Each night, she told me stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我穿越了无数光年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I traveled light-years…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（端点星）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心不断扩大 容下越来越多的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my mind expanding to hold more and more worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我从未到达端点星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I never reached Terminus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:02:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远离文明、荒无人烟的边缘地带\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Straddling the farthest reaches of civilization, unsettled by man…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是帝国的尽头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it was the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对那里的故事一无所知 直到许多年后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And its story remained dark to me until many years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到它变成我的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until it became my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到它变成…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until it became…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the only story.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-别这样 -抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Don't do that. -Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-其他人呢  -我们在围栏和他们会合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Where are the others? -We're meeting them at the fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有点迟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're a bit late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-吉雅 -太多岩石了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Gia! -It's so rocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主教爪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A bishop's claw.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-在上谷附近 -我们得小声点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Up-valley. -We need to be real quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空域从那边开始 靠近那块岩石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The null field starts all the way up there. Near that rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们称之为“穹窿”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They called it "the Vault."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有殖民者都很清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the colonists knew for certain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在周围投射了一个阻止人们靠近的力场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was that it projected a field designed to keep people away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人能突破\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one could breach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你先去 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, you gonna go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你先吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought you were first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:03:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你先去 到达岩石后面 放下你的标记\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You go first and put your marker past the rock,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我就让你碰我的一边胸部 -吉雅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'll let you touch my tit. -Gia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十秒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者你可以看两边胸部 看30秒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or you can look at 'em both for 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你向月亮发誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Swear on your moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄严发誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Four-sworn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你赢了也得不到好处 -我能看到他尿裤子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You get nothing if you win. -Get to watch him piss his pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He isn't gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 凯尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Keir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你弟弟是个废物爪子 -吉雅 别笑他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Your brother is an assclaw. -Gia, stop laughing at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:05:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他真可悲 -我差点就到了 我很接近了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-He's pathetic. -I was almost there. I was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利 你要去哪 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poly, where you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-该死 波利 -波利 回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Shit. Poly! -Poly, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们没做交易 -我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-We don't have a deal. -I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见幽灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanna see the ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-波利 -他不动了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Poly? -He's not moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们得去找帮手 -那你干嘛站着不动 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-We gotta get help. -What you standing there for then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都走了 吃吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're all gone. Eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见幽灵了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw the ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看见的是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该转身回去 像你的朋友凯尔一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should've turned back, like your boy Keir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人因试图接近那里而受伤 真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People who've tried to get closer have been hurt. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你保持着纪录 但你没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got the record and you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的标记那么远 从没有人见过它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your mark is so far, no one's ever seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为它不存在 幽灵也不存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's because it doesn't exist. And neither does the ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守卫者 你觉得它什么时候 会向我们展示它的身份 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When do you think it's going to tell us what it is, Warden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以叫我塞佛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Call me Salvor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为它在乎我们 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you assume it cares anything about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它才不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法接近它的不只有人类 任何生物都不行 鸟、昆虫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not just people it keeps away. It's everything. It's birds, insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没有人突破空域 以后也不会有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one's ever gotten through the null field, and no one ever will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它警告我们远离 所以别冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's warning us to stay away. So stop tempting fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 路上小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那边有一只主教爪… -在上谷 我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-There's a bishop's claw-- -Up-valley. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞佛哈定、候伯马洛、骡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salvor Hardin. Hober Mallow. The Mule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（川陀）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天我将认识这些名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would learn these names one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（35年前）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了拯救人类而抗争的英雄和恶徒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The heroes and villains fighting for the salvation of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要想了解我们的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But to understand our future,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须铭记过去和那些创造历史的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we have to remember the past and the ones who caused it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位数学家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A mathematician.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位殉道者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A martyr.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位谋杀犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有最重要的人物 哈里谢顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the most important player of all, Hari Seldon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很快就会上路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She'll be on her way soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会好起来的 瑞驰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It will all work out, Raych.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都在消亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything is dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不意味着最后不会好起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That doesn't mean it won't all work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否曾希望有其他的方式 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you ever wish there was another way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都希望 孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every day, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在是最佳时机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But this is the optimal time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（辛纳克斯）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,86960947\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}86,960,947.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,86960957\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}86,960,957.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,86960971\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}86,960,971.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-86960987 -时间到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-86,960,987-- -It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖尔 你准备好了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gaal? Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一辈子都向外眺望 梦想着自己生活在别处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All my life, I looked out and dreamed of being somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我意识到我会有多想念眼前的景色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now I realize how much I'll miss this view.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须牢牢记住这个画面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to remember it perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你不必这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以向先知祭司们呈请\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can petition the Seer priests.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在止步还不迟 现在决定留下还不迟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not too late for you to stop this. It's not too late for you to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里已经容不下我了 妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no place for me here anymore, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果留下 我会死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll die if I stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我在川陀将是安全的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But on Trantor, I'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人所接纳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昂起你的头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold your head high.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都憎恨我 你不恨我吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They all hate me. You don't hate me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会 盖尔 我永远都爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never, Gaal. I'll always love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我人生最大的喜悦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My greatest joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在外面会迷失自己的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'd be lost out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go, child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转移指令启动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beginning transfer sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请移动至跃迁舱 准备上路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please move to jumppods and secure for travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了什么话吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 但我本想问你 这是不是你第一次搭乘帝国跃迁舰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. But I was going to ask if this was your first time on an imperial jumpship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是的 我有点紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. It is. I'm a bit nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手放在屏幕上就可以了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just place your hand on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-它会扫描你的参数 -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-And it will scan your metrics. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-杰瑞尔 -盖尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Jerril. -Gaal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛纳克斯人 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Synnax?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得出你有一点口音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Picked up just a hint of it in your accent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在核心区很少听到这种口音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't hear it much at the Core,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有时会去银河系边缘的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I travel near the rim worlds sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出把祷告石移除的那个人技术很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whoever took the prayer stones out did a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不仔细看都看不到疤痕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wouldn't see the scars if you didn't know to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我太无礼了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry if I overstepped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不受影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It doesn't screw me up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有些人在跃迁之后会有宿醉感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but some people come out of the jump feeling a little hungover.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喝酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父母从前常常潜水采海藻 所以我们很早就起床\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My parents dove an algae farm, and we woke up pretty early.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会确保你全程保持睡眠状态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're gonna sleep through this. They make sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跃迁期间 他们不能启动重力 我不知道为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They can't have the grav on during the jump. I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力产生器输出的引力波\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, the grav generators output a waveform
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会削弱跃迁驱动器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that corrupts the jumpdrive's ability
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跨维度速度下标绘四维节点的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to plot fourth-dimensional points at transdimensional speeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么去川陀 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you going to Trantor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将与哈里谢顿共事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going to work with Hari Seldon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.91,0:13:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赢得了一场数学竞赛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won a math contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 哈里谢顿 而且你来自辛纳克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wow. Hari Seldon. And you from Synnax.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是个很大型的竞赛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a pretty big contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始跃迁 三、二、一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commencing jump in three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会醒来 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在跃迁期间全程沉睡 真可惜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a pity we have to sleep through the jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说外面的光很美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's supposed to be quite the light show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你不是太空人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if you're not a Spacer,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身体和大脑可能无法保持一致\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you can find your body and mind taking different trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从头睡到尾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I slept through the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅程即将结束 请准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}…and prepare to disembark.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说帝国有哪方面在行 那就是建筑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the Empire is good for anything, they can damn well build.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壮观\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到川陀 帝国中心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome to Trantor, the eye of the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请心怀尊敬 享受和平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please respect and enjoy the peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:16:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是士兵吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are those soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的世界大概不算新闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Probably didn't make the news on your world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但银河边缘地带发生了一些冲突\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}some sort of kerfuffle at the galaxy's edge,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安纳克里昂和狄斯比斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anacreon and Thespis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国评鉴师在交火过程中受牵连了 所以现在这成了一件大事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Imperial appraisers got caught in the cross fire, so now it's a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保证人和联络方式 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sponsor and contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里谢顿博士 斯璀璘大学\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dr. Hari Seldon. Streeling University.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返回母星时间 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Expected return to home planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会回去 这里是我的家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not going back. This is my home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可搭乘轨道上的任意车厢 请心怀尊敬 享受和平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any car on the stalk. Please respect and enjoy the peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我对你有了一点了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now that I know you a little better,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不浪费口舌为你解释一切了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't waste my breath explaining everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但接下来很棒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This part is great though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请前往任何可用车厢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please make your way to any available car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本车厢即将开始沿着轨道下降\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This car will commence its descent down the stalk momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直保持清醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna stay awake the whole ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从川陀站下降至星球地表需要14个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It takes 14 hours to drop from Trantor Station to the planet's surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过严格说来那不是地表\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Although, technically, it's not the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数十亿的居民在川陀外层之下居住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Billions of citizens spend their lives beneath Trantor's outer shell,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地底下100层忙碌一辈子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}toiling away on a hundred subterranean levels
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来都见不到太阳或星星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without ever seeing the sun or the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然世界仅存的一切都属于帝王们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever remained of the natural world belonged to the Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白昼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:18:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一脉相承的王朝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Genetic Dynasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处于不同年纪的克里昂一世克隆人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clones of Cleon I, decanted at different ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧里奥师傅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Master Orlio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为我们工作多少年了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long have you worked for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为大帝工作已有68年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sixty-eight privileged years, Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从12岁开始清理壁画时起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Started cleaning the Mural when I was 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今已经从一端到另一端清理了四次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gone from one end to the other four times over since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一个颜色已经熟记在心了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Know every grain of chroma by heart now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 有些颜色是否更难清洁 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me, are there some colors more resistant to cleaning than others?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫红色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Plum.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长春花色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Periwinkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏红色尤其棘手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Saffron is a particularly truculent pigment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血红色呢 是不是也棘手 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about crimson? Is crimson truculent?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's come to our attention
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的居所发现了哈里谢顿著的文章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that a tract authored by Hari Seldon was discovered in your quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 大帝 是我愚钝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Apologies, Empire. It was foolish of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just that I'd--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听人提到他的主张 感到好奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Heard whispers of his proclamations and were curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们把谢顿称为“乌鸦嘴” 是吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They refer to Seldon as "the Raven," don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说他对帝国有不少批评\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hear he's rather critical of the Imperium.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴地向您报告 他的文字都是毫无根据的垃圾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm happy to report that his words are baseless trash,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再补充一点 用词狂妄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and atrociously written, if I might add.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此 这个男人已聚集了一帮信众\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nevertheless, the man has amassed a following.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们把希望寄托在 乌鸦嘴谢顿说的每个字词上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People who hinge their hopes on every word Raven Seldon utters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言语是星星之火 可以燎原 欧里奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Words have a way of fanning into wildfires, Orlio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忠诚不二 大帝 我绝不会…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am loyal, Empire. I would never--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你不会 所以我才亲自找你谈论这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you won't, which is why I broached this subject in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empire--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:21:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明兄弟 你今早学了什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are your lessons this morning, Brother Dawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外围星域的王国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Outer Reach kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我学会了一首安纳克里昂的古老歌曲 是关于狩猎的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I learned an old Anacreon song about hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐中往往藏着真理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, there is much truth in music.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个男孩用刀划开小鹿的皮肉 将它的身体作为庇护所\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A boy bleeds a fawn with a knife and then takes shelter in her coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一首并不是狩猎歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That one's not really a hunting song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一首淫曲 唱的是男孩与女人的初夜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a dirty song about a boy's first time with a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你脑中再唱一次 别把两者混淆了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Play it back in your mind. And don't confuse the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白昼兄弟 请把孔雀留给厨师处理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brother Day, please leave the peacock to the cooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不亲自动手 你的自传也仍然会很有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll be no less fascinating to your biographers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏兄弟认为我这么做 是为了让自己更有吸引力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brother Dusk imagines I do this to be colorful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白昼兄弟总是曲解我的话 却不曲解禽肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Brother Day puts more words in my mouth than he does poultry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是猪油\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the lard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨师在烤肉之前用针把猪油注入皮下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The cooks inject it under the skin with a needle right before roasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-知道为什么他们用针吗  -因为更高效 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Do you know why they use a needle? -Because it's efficient?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们担心如果用刀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because they're afraid if they use a knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种传统的方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as is the time-honored way,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能会划破孔雀皮 那我就会把他们送到50层下的炖肉锅里去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they might rip the skin, and I'll send them to a stew-pot stall 50 levels down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这确实是个大问题 为什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All of which is a problem. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为当人们担心自己做好本职时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because when people are afraid to do their job right,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一定会出错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they're certain to do it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这叫管理不当 -这叫烤得不当的孔雀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-That's poor stewardship. -It's poor roast peacock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是每一件事都可以总结出道理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not everything is a teachable moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.04,0:22:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德默泽尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Demerzel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.79,0:22:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄斯比斯和安纳克里昂的使团即将到达\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The delegations from Thespis and Anacreon are arriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他们看起来如何  -脾气暴躁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-How did they seem? -Peevish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.71,0:22:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一帮蛮族 麻烦很多 价值很少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Barbarian kingdoms. They're more trouble than they're worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.88,0:22:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让外围星域贸易局 把关税预测资料带到寝宫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have Outer Reach Trade bring tariff projections to the residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.35,0:22:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿得体面些 让人为你梳理头发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dress nice. Have someone brush your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.39,0:22:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我们本周最重要的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not the most important thing we'll do this week,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却是他们这辈子最重要的一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it's the most important thing they'll do in their lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.13,0:23:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安纳克里昂和狄斯比斯 观察两方的举止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anacreon and Thespis. Observe the mannerisms of each party.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.76,0:23:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们憎恨对方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They hate each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.06,0:23:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是不共戴天的仇敌 但战争的代价高昂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their enmity is legendary. But war is expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.86,0:23:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们召他们过来加以谴责 令双方达成和解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And so we have called them onto the carpet to broker a peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你的陪伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks for the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.29,0:23:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你的新工作一切顺利 希望哈里谢顿值得你这么远来到这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good luck with the new job. I hope Hari Seldon is worth the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.75,0:23:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.05,0:23:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺帅的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.64,0:23:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞驰…你在哪里 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raych, Raych, Raych. Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.73,0:24:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那就是我 -什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-That's me. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.40,0:24:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 瑞驰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's me, Raych.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.70,0:24:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在哈里手下做事 谢顿博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I work for Hari. Dr. Seldon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.16,0:24:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-行李领取处在这边 -不用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Baggage Claim is this way. -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.79,0:24:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我的行李都在这\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. This is all I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.66,0:24:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.46,0:24:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请跟我来 参观本星球其他地方吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then the rest of planet is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.92,0:24:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是完美的复制品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's supposed to be a perfect replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.59,0:24:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们在地下的人不会知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not that we'd know under the outer shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.09,0:24:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,64层的一半区域 都是服务器投放的天空影像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Half of level 64 is just servers running skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.39,0:24:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川陀这里还有先知教堂吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there still a Seer church here on Trantor?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.56,0:24:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下面应该有 在22层\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Down there, I think. Level 22.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.44,0:24:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.20,0:24:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.74,0:24:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, I've--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.66,0:25:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没见过来自辛纳克斯的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never met anyone from Synnax before.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.42,0:25:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现共情与管理精神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An expression of compassion and stewardship,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.34,0:25:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是魂之壁画\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Mural of Souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.80,0:25:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每日都由一脉相承的王朝资深人员打理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}worked on every day by the senior member of the Genetic Dynasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.76,0:25:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壁画描绘了四个世纪的和平和银行家族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Mural depicts the four-century age of peace and the Galactic Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.44,0:25:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到动态的颜色吗 色彩轻微地移动 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Notice the active chroma? How the pigment subtly moves?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.11,0:25:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星省使者赞登\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Provincial Ambassador Xandem.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.57,0:25:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对壁画有什么问题或评论吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you have a question or a comment about the Mural?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.45,0:25:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是在感叹帝国的仁爱之心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were just marveling at the Empire's benevolent reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.83,0:25:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为确实令人惊叹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For it is a marvel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.09,0:25:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,86963537\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}86,963,537.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.76,0:25:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,86963549\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}86,963,549.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.05,0:25:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,86963563\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}86,963,563.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.51,0:26:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,963567\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}963,567.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.35,0:26:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,86963573\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}86,963,573…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.15,0:26:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你在祈祷吗  -不是 为什么这么问 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Are you praying? -No. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.53,0:26:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的嘴唇在动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your lips were moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.65,0:26:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我感到紧张时会数质数\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. When I'm nervous, I count primes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.33,0:26:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里说你会想看这个的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hari said you'd wanna see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.02,0:26:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖尔 这位是哈里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gaal, meet Hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.90,0:26:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢顿博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dr. Seldon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.28,0:26:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你邀请我来这里 我感到很荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am so honored you invited me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.91,0:26:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得帝国图书馆如何 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you think of the Imperial Library?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.82,0:27:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太惊人了 这么多书在一个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's amazing. So many books in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.83,0:27:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜在辛纳克斯很难找到书\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I imagine books were hard to come by on Synnax.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.04,0:27:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.42,0:27:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道卡里的第九条折叠定理证明吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, you know Kalle's Ninth Proof of Folding?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.47,0:27:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 如果没有它 我不可能解出亚布拉克萨斯猜想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I couldn't have solved Abraxas without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.47,0:27:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人都没想到使用这条证明 500年来从未有人这么做过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one else thought to use it. Not in 500 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.94,0:27:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为原因是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.23,0:27:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡里的文字充满诗意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kalle's writing is poetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.86,0:27:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美 但是很难想象其内容严谨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's beautiful, but it's hard to imagine there's any rigor there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.94,0:27:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以学者们不会读她的作品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So serious scholars don't read her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.99,0:27:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么读呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.58,0:27:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最初读卡里的作品 是为了寻找她文字中的韵律\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I went to Kalle for the rhythm of the words at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.00,0:27:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有注意到数学的部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I missed the math.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.00,0:27:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但当我体会文字背后的意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But when I read between the lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.33,0:27:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我意识到她提出了一个激进的理论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I realized she was proposing a radical theory
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.09,0:27:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于非阿基米德局部域的整数环\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about rings of integers in non-Archimedean local fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.26,0:27:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Indeed she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.05,0:28:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我很好奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It does make me wonder, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.59,0:28:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一开始是如何 发现卡里的第九条证明的 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how you've managed to stumble across Kalle's Ninth Proof in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.52,0:28:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到你身处的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}given where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.64,0:28:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是辛纳克斯 盖尔 在这里 好奇心不是一种罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't Synnax, Gaal. Curiosity isn't a crime here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.11,0:28:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很孤独\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.53,0:28:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里几乎没有人像我一样思考\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Almost no one there thought like I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.24,0:28:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是数学不看立场 不会品头论足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But math doesn't take sides. It doesn't judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.58,0:28:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样聪明 在那样一个地方一定感到孤独\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I imagine you were lonely, a mind like yours in a place like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.63,0:28:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是卡里的证明原稿 以她的母语特莱克斯语写的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kalle's original proof manuscript. Written in her native Thraxian.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.61,0:29:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天他们会逮捕我和你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're going to arrest me tomorrow. And you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.86,0:29:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -几乎已经确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What? -It's almost a certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.07,0:29:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕 为什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Arrest? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.74,0:29:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会发生的概率非零 但那个数字小得不值得讨论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a nonzero chance it won't happen. But it's not a number worth discussing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.21,0:29:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这一定是哪里出了错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. This has to be a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.92,0:29:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人会说谎 盖尔 数字不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People lie, Gaal. Numbers don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.79,0:29:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你熟悉我在心理历史学方面的研究 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you familiar with my work? Psychohistory?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.76,0:29:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-每个数学家都读过你的… -你认同那个概念吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Every mathematician has read your-- -Do you agree with the concept?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.63,0:29:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理论上是 但我不知道这和…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In theory. But I don't know what it has to do with--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.09,0:29:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是理论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not a theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.47,0:29:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是以数字形式表现的人类命运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the destiny of the human race expressed in numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.72,0:29:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是帝国将逮捕我们的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it's the reason the Empire will take us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.98,0:29:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们担心你能预知未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're worried you can predict the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.85,0:29:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们担心人们相信我能预知未来 他们不喜欢我所预知的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're worried people believe I can. And they don't like the future I predict.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.07,0:29:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那未来是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.44,0:29:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川陀将被摧毁 帝国将灭亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trantor is going to be destroyed. The Empire will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.66,0:29:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该明白 这些并不是我急于想告诉人们的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You understand, these aren't things I'm anxious to tell people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.99,0:29:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是数学告诉我的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just what the math tells me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.54,0:29:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么让我大老远过来 只为了逮捕我 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why let me come all this way just to arrest me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.00,0:29:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个好问题 你告诉我答案吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a good question. You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.99,0:30:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我解出了亚布拉克萨斯猜想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I solved Abraxas.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.70,0:30:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们认为只有我能证明你是错的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They think I'm the only one who can prove you wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.12,0:30:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实只有你能证明我错了 但我没有错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you are, if I was. But I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.25,0:30:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带我观光时知道这一切吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you know all this when you were showing me the sights?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.71,0:30:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事关重大 远比你想象得复杂 盖尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's more at stake here than you can imagine, Gaal.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.13,0:30:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我冒着生命危险来到这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I risked my life coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.05,0:30:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你希望我再冒一次险 只为了支持你的计算结果 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now you want me to risk it again just to support your numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.35,0:30:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得不完全准确 对吧 盖尔 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not entirely accurate, is it, Gaal?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.18,0:30:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你离开辛纳克斯也是为了不被逮捕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You left Synnax one step ahead of arrest yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.85,0:31:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你知道数学从来都不只是数字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you know math is never just numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.77,0:31:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被错的人掌握 它会变成武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the wrong hands, it's a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.94,0:31:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被对的人掌握 就是解放\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the right hands, deliverance.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.07,0:31:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.24,0:31:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.91,0:31:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们应该会用大半个晚上定位你的酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It should take them most of the night to divine your hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.75,0:31:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很快会再见面的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll talk soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.88,0:31:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你来这里不是为了这个奖品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know it's not the prize you came here for…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.59,0:31:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但目前只能送你这个了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it will have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.05,0:31:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不能收下 -当然能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I can't keep this. -Of course you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.55,0:31:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这栋建筑总有一天会烧成灰烬 偷走它是慈悲之举\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This building will burn one day. Stealing is a mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.45,0:31:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我读过他的所有心理历史学研究\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've read all his work, psychohistory.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.66,0:31:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没想过他会以这种方式应用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just never imagined he'd use it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.79,0:31:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国不会伤害你的 他们需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Empire isn't gonna hurt you. They need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.83,0:32:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并不确定这一点 他也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't know that. And neither does he.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.92,0:32:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-盖尔 -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Gaal-- -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.00,0:32:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没见过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You haven't seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.05,0:32:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一个星球要你死 你一定会死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When a planet wants you dead, you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.17,0:32:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外围星域安纳克里昂星 使者赞登\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ambassador Xandem, Planet Anacreon, Outer Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.06,0:32:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.81,0:32:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以塔林森林最古老的树木雕刻而成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Carved from the oldest tree in the Tallyn Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.94,0:32:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一块木材也用于雕刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The same wood used to carve the bow
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.78,0:32:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安纳克里昂最伟大的猎手拉肯柯恩的弓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of Anacreon's greatest hunter, Larken Keaen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.49,0:32:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 使者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Ambassador.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.45,0:32:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢魂之壁画吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you enjoy the Mural of Souls?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.37,0:32:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 大帝 我从未见过这样的壁画\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, Empire. I have never seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.50,0:32:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外围星域狄斯比斯星 荣誉外交官舍恩舍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Honored Diplomat Shae Un Shae, Planet Thespis, Outer Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.34,0:32:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.14,0:32:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄斯比斯之《洗礼经》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A Thespin Book of Ablution.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.30,0:32:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的金属丝饰是最近新锻造的 为了向帝国的和平致敬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The filigree was recently smithed to honor the imperial peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.39,0:33:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 荣誉外交官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Honored Diplomat.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.85,0:33:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢两个使团来到川陀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And thank you, both delegations, for making the journey to Trantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.40,0:33:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你们别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not that you had a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.82,0:33:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九个世纪以来 安铎星带协议 为你们的星球带来和平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For nine centuries, the Anthor Belt Agreement served your planets well.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.62,0:33:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年 狄斯比斯发现了一颗异常小行星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Last year, Thespis identified a rogue asteroid,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.20,0:33:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们认为它从协议规管的区域漂移至区外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which they believe drifted from the area governed by the agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.33,0:33:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有正式的立场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We took no official position.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.50,0:33:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只表达我们一成的意见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just our 10%.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.84,0:33:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安纳克里昂认为狄斯比斯的举动有违协议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anacreon believes Thespis acts in bad faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.59,0:33:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国认为帝国的臣民的血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Empire believes imperial blood has been shed
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.85,0:33:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已洒在离家五万光年的一块冷岩上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on a cold rock 50,000 light-years from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.77,0:33:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这三种想法中的任何一种 都曾引致上千次战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For any of these three beliefs, a thousand wars have been fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.36,0:33:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的几天我们将判定 是否将有另一场战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The next days will determine if there will be another.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.62,0:34:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心怀尊敬 享受和平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Respect and enjoy the peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.62,0:34:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心怀尊敬 享受和平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Respect and enjoy the peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.34,0:34:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明兄弟 你的想法是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brother Dawn, what do you make of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.81,0:34:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄斯比斯人想提醒你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Thespins want to remind you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.48,0:34:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安铎星带小行星对他们的信仰有多重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how important the Anthor Belt asteroids are to their religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.10,0:34:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看这个金属丝饰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But look there. In the metal filigree.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.07,0:34:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个徽章的图案是以重金属钯制成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The pattern in the sigil is made of heavy palladium.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.28,0:34:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是异常小行星的金属 你觉得它占了徽章的多大比例 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The metal from the rogue asteroid. How much would you say of the sigil?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.07,0:34:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-五分之一  -接近四分之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Maybe a fifth of it? -Closer to a quarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.29,0:34:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前 狄斯比斯人将他们十分之一的矿石 作为宗教税提供给我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Currently, the Thespins tithe 10% of the mined ore to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.71,0:34:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是他们用低调的方式表示\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is their way of quietly saying
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.42,0:34:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们站在他们那边 他们愿意将比例提高到25%\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they'll go all the way to 25% if we side with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.88,0:34:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里完全没有金属 连箭头都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no metal here at all. Not even in the arrow tips.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.05,0:34:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 为什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's right. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.05,0:35:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安纳克里昂人需要钯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Anacreons need palladium.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.56,0:35:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们没有任何钯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They have none.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.06,0:35:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像狩猎歌一样 和狩猎完全无关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's like the hunting song. It's not at all about hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.61,0:35:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艺术不过是听起来更优美的政治\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Art is simply politics' sweeter tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.82,0:35:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外围星域的风俗也许显得奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The customs of the Outer Reach may seem idiosyncratic.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.78,0:35:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们对于细节的一丝不苟 是我们维系和平的方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But our attention to detail is how we maintain the peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.28,0:35:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果人们不守规矩 我们就用武力镇压\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if the people step out of line, we hit them with a big stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.21,0:35:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.25,0:35:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢顿和那女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seldon and the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.97,0:35:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在动用武力上不用顾虑太多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't overthink the stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.59,0:35:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先知教堂 我们有时间去吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Seer church. Do we have time?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.10,0:35:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.57,0:35:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可以坐下 他站着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She can sit. He will stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.40,0:36:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他必须解除武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he will need to disarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.66,0:36:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异教徒和我将进行对话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The heretic and I will talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.76,0:36:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉醒之际\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Upon awakening…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.43,0:36:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉醒之际\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Upon awakening…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.05,0:36:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们说出言语\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We speak the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.89,0:36:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言语让我们被看见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the words make us seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.06,0:36:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我是谁吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.81,0:36:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她把脸上的沉睡者之语除去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that she has torn the Sleeper's words from her face
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.56,0:36:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此不能被上帝所看见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and can't be seen by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.82,0:36:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你知道我是谁吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.65,0:36:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她解开了一个最古老的谜语\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She has solved one of life's ancient puzzles
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.15,0:36:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在解开谜语的过程中令生命的价值贬值\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and cheapened the worth of life in the solving.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.49,0:36:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.20,0:36:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在辛纳克斯 她几乎和她信奉的新神 谢顿一样出名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On Synnax, she is almost as famous as her new god, Seldon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.71,0:36:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他不是神 -对 他不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-He's not a god. -No, he is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.00,0:37:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他将像所有与他一样的人那样死去 上帝看不见的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He will die as all men like him die, unseen by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.30,0:37:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的信徒也一样 她也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As will his followers. As will she.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.76,0:37:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖尔多尼克 我只会说一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gaal Dornick. I'll say this once,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.73,0:37:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是这个被抛弃的世界里 最高位、也是唯一的先知祭司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I am the highest-ranking and only Seer priest on this forsaken world.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.19,0:37:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你陷入困境 我能帮助你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you are in trouble, I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.74,0:37:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你想要的吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.43,0:37:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要我留下吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want me to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.06,0:37:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样他们就不会逮捕我吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will that stop them from arresting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.31,0:37:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.86,0:37:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.11,0:38:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-回头见 -会吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'll see you. -Will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.44,0:38:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.53,0:38:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人想在走前再祈祷一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some like to pray one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.45,0:38:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么做了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.74,0:38:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.37,0:39:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得她怎么样 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you make of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.66,0:39:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们还没找上她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They haven't gotten to her yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.54,0:39:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时还没\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.38,0:39:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得她怎么样 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you make of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.71,0:39:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是靠自己解开亚布拉克萨斯猜想的 这点我很肯定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She solved Abraxas on her own. I'm sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.17,0:39:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于另一个问题嘛 我们以后会知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As for the other question, well, we shall see.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.35,0:40:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是楼斯艾法金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My name's Lors Avakim.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.40,0:40:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哈里让我来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hari sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.57,0:40:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪里 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.03,0:40:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逮捕了 如他所预测的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Arrested. As he predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.82,0:40:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩都被指控严重叛国罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've both been charged with high treason,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.99,0:40:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密谋危害帝国的稳定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}conspiracy to destabilize the Imperium.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.00,0:41:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一场噩梦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.66,0:41:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里希望你知道 将你牵涉进来 他感到非常抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hari wants you to know how sorry he is for involving you in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.92,0:41:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是他的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.51,0:41:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.76,0:41:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以无顾忌地说话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can speak freely now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.18,0:41:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国得知哈里的结论后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once the Imperium learned of Hari's conclusions,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.85,0:41:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有掩饰他们干扰项目的意图\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they made no secret of trying to disrupt the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.60,0:41:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里是让我来做饵的吗  因为我可以证明他是错的 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did Hari bring me here as bait? Because I can prove him wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.27,0:41:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没有错 多尼克女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not wrong, Ms. Dornick.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.19,0:41:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是做饵的猜测是正确的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But yes on the bait part.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.13,0:41:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.59,0:41:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钩得很疼 但我努力保持不动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The hook hurts, but I'm trying not to wriggle too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.10,0:42:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体起立\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.06,0:42:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里昂12世审判庭开庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The tribunal of Cleon XII is convened.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.44,0:42:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尊贵的大人 有罪者哈里谢顿博士和盖尔多尼克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your Exalted, the offenders, Dr. Hari Seldon and Gaal Dornick,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.53,0:42:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被指控犯下如此严重的罪行 不仅威胁川陀的和平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are accused of crimes so grave that they threaten not just Trantor
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.33,0:42:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也危及整个银河的存亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the entire galaxy's existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.33,0:42:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将证明谢顿博士和他的信众\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will prove that Dr. Seldon and his followers
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.54,0:42:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参与了密谋 目的为摧毁民众对帝国的信心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}engaged in a conspiracy designed to destroy the confidence in our empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.59,0:42:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢顿博士 请起立\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dr. Seldon. Will you rise?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.89,0:42:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原本来自赫利肯星 是吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You hail from the world of Helicon, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.60,0:42:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.89,0:42:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能陈述你目前在川陀的职位吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will you state your current position here on Trantor?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.48,0:42:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是斯璀璘大学的概率理论学教授\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm a professor of probability theory at Streeling University.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.44,0:42:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体而言 是心理历史学范畴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Specifically, the area of psychohistory.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.11,0:42:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请为我们界定一下这个词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Define that for us, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.90,0:42:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心理历史学是一种预测模型\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Psychohistory is a predictive model
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.66,0:43:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用于预测大基数人口的行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}designed to forecast the behavior of very large populations.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.29,0:43:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单说来 你声称自己能够预测未来 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In plainspoken terms, you claim to be able to predict the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.33,0:43:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法预知你的晚餐将吃什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I don't know what you're going to have for dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.88,0:43:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你问的是这个意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if that's what you're asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.34,0:43:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白我问的是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what I'm asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.01,0:43:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河帝国中有八万亿人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Galactic Empire comprises some eight trillion individuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.89,0:43:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这个基数 大到足以作为预测的样本吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you say that was a large enough sample to make a prediction?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.89,0:43:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.97,0:43:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于这个样本 你作出了预测吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And do you have a prediction for that particular sample?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.77,0:43:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.32,0:43:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Indulge us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.73,0:43:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川陀和银河帝国将在五个世纪内化为废墟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trantor and the Galactic Empire will lie in ruins within five centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.20,0:43:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肃静 各位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Silence, brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.70,0:43:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假定你的说法正确 你能证明它是真的吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Accepting your statement for the moment, can you prove it's true?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.41,0:43:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能向另一位熟悉序数分析的数学家证明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only to another mathematician conversant in ordinal analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.34,0:43:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真省事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.30,0:43:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的真理如此晦涩 以至于几乎所有民众都无法理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your truths are so esoteric they escape the grasp of nearly every citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.26,0:44:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我的真理 是科学的真理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're not my truths. They belong to science.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.97,0:44:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国的历史长达一万两千年 博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Imperium is 12,000 years old, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.31,0:44:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们真的能相信 它会在短短500年内消失 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are we really to believe that it could be gone in just 500?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.31,0:44:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-也许更快 -更快 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Maybe quicker. -Quicker?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.23,0:44:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腐朽的树干看上去茁壮 但一场风暴就能让它断为两截\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A rotten tree trunk appears strong until the storm breaks it in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.28,0:44:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到近期外围星域的纷乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Consider recent events in the Outer Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.41,0:44:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来这里不是要考虑其他…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not here to consider any other--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.24,0:44:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你们必须考虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you must!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.66,0:44:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国将灭亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Empire will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.12,0:44:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社会将失序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Order will vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.29,0:44:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星际战争将无穷无尽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Interstellar wars will be endless.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.00,0:44:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无数世界化为辐射尘埃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ten thousand worlds reduced to radioactive cinders.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.39,0:44:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们做的一切都无法避免它的到来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing we do can prevent this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.22,0:44:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…蛮荒时期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This… period of barbarism.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.27,0:44:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为它将维持多久 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long do you claim it will last?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.19,0:44:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三万年 律师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thirty thousand years, Advocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.78,0:45:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我谨此呈报法庭 谢顿博士所谓的“预测”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I submit to the court that Dr. Seldon's "predictions"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.99,0:45:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上是为了摧毁公众的信念\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are actually intended to destroy public confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.70,0:45:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是革命分子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not a revolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.12,0:45:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, then what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.62,0:45:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经说了未来无法改变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've already said the future cannot be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.92,0:45:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你究竟是为了什么目的 进行这个项目 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what exactly is the purpose of your project?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.21,0:45:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想降低这场毁灭的破坏力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm trying to soften the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.64,0:45:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭无可避免\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It cannot be prevented,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.26,0:45:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将受到一次又一次大事件的冲击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this mass of events rushing to meet us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.98,0:45:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们可以缩短灭亡后黑暗纪元的长度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we can shorten the dark ages that follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.73,0:45:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缩短多少 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.23,0:45:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们采纳你的计划 能缩短多少 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we embrace your plan, how much?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.32,0:45:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该会面临一千年的黑暗 律师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We should be in the dark for a thousand years, Advocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.24,0:45:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样 那我们应感谢诸神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if that is all, we should thank the gods for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.14,0:46:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我不叫杰瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My name's not really Jerril.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.94,0:46:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你可以继续这么叫我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you can keep calling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.81,0:46:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经观察你一段时间了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've been watching you for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.81,0:46:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实从你解开 亚布拉克萨斯猜想那刻起就开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From the moment you solved the Abraxas Conjecture, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.74,0:46:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你带了一份礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I brought you a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.65,0:46:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他称之为元光体 很美吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He calls it the Prime Radiant. It's beautiful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.28,0:46:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说里面包含他对帝国的所有预测\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He claims it contains all of his predictions concerning the Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.37,0:46:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以数学等式的形式表现出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}expressed as a mathematical equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.66,0:46:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他允许你查看吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did he allow you to examine it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.38,0:46:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.21,0:46:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得那很奇怪 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, don't you think that's curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.96,0:46:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他创造了一个深奥的理论 整个银河都没有人能理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He devises a theory so opaque that no one in the galaxy can understand it,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.05,0:46:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当他找到一个能理解的人时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and when he finds an individual who can,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.30,0:46:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却不允许她一探究竟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he doesn't allow her a look behind the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.26,0:46:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.68,0:46:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为历史上充满江湖骗子和虚假先知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because history is littered with charlatans and false messiahs.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.35,0:46:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他说的是真的呢  如果心理历史学是真的呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if he's telling the truth? What if psychohistory is real?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.23,0:46:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他的等式有错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If his equations are flawed,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.02,0:47:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在道德上 你有义务揭露错误\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you have a moral obligation to expose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.45,0:47:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果等式正确呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if they hold true?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.20,0:47:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否认它的真实性 然后回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Disavow them and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.62,0:47:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保证 大帝一定会找到途径 向你表达他的感谢之情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I promise you, Empire will find a way to express his gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.17,0:47:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就长话短说吧 盖尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll make the calculus simple for you, Gaal.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.38,0:47:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你说哈里是骗子 他会死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you say Hari's a liar, he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.97,0:47:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不这么说 你会死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you don't, you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.26,0:47:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们就采用鸵鸟政策 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, we should just all bury our heads in the sand then?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.97,0:47:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他的公式正确\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If his equations hold true,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.89,0:47:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大帝会以我们一直以来的方式 着手解决问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then Empire will set about solving the problem as we always have,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.27,0:47:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不必惊吓到数万亿人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without terrifying trillions of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.10,0:47:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该信任你这个间谍的话 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I should believe in you, a spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.77,0:47:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该信任建筑起川陀的头脑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should believe in the minds that built Trantor,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.28,0:47:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们建造了跃迁驱动器、星桥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}built the jumpdrive, that built the Star Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.53,0:47:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们那里 这样的人叫科学家 而不是政客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where I come from, they call those scientists, not politicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.03,0:47:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你来自哪里 盖尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know where you come from, Gaal.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.24,0:47:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的人叫异教徒 全被溺死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They were called heretics and drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.79,0:48:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道跃迁舰上发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I also know what happened on the jumpship.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.67,0:48:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跃迁期间…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}During the jump…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.05,0:48:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是清醒的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you were awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.88,0:48:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.51,0:48:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你为什么要对我说谎  -不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Why did you lie to me about it? -I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.02,0:48:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.43,0:48:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What does?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.06,0:48:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕自己与众不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Being different.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.02,0:48:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都是不同的 多尼克女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're all different, Ms. Dornick.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.36,0:48:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的姐姐长到七岁才开口说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My sister didn't speak until she was seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.28,0:48:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只会说名词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And even then, just nouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.57,0:48:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you're something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.11,0:48:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不知道自己哪里不一样 我希望你尽快找到答案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you don't know what it is, I urge you to figure it out
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.78,0:48:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁其他人还没发现它 并以此作为攻击你的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before someone else does and uses it against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.59,0:49:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你声称你的计划能够缓解即将来临的黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You claim your plan can reduce the coming darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.09,0:49:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做到 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.18,0:49:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传言古人曾建造一个智库 存放全世界的知识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The ancients are rumored to have built a repository for the world's wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.22,0:49:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说那个智库已被燃烧成灰烬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}According to myth, it burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.89,0:49:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所建议的方式是非集中式的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm proposing something less centralized.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.35,0:49:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《银河百科全书》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An Encyclopedia Galactica.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.02,0:49:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灭亡后 文明从灰烬中重生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After the fall, as civilization climbs from the ashes,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.28,0:49:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来的世世代代将在此之上重建文明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the coming generations will have something to build upon,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.53,0:49:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个基地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.79,0:50:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不需要从零开始 知识已经存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They won't have to reinvent the wheel. The knowledge will already exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.17,0:50:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们需要拯救的不仅仅是知识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it isn't just knowledge we'd be saving,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.34,0:50:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是人类的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but humanity's story.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.92,0:50:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our story.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.26,0:50:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川陀已经有一座帝国图书馆了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trantor already has an imperial library.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.93,0:50:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能矗立多久呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For how long?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.52,0:50:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这番言论确实触及问题的关键\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, that statement does bring us to the heart of the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.60,0:50:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你可以向熟悉序数分析的人 证明你的理论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said you could prove your theorem to someone conversant in ordinal analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.90,0:50:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖尔多尼克 请起立\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gaal Dornick, please rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.82,0:50:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你走到审判台前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Approach the dais, if you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.37,0:50:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来自辛纳克斯 是吗  我们应该说明这点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're from Synnax, correct? We should say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.21,0:50:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.34,0:50:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你移除了你的祷告石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've had your prayer stones removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.38,0:50:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的外表看起来几乎和我们一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You almost look like one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.55,0:50:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据我了解 在你的世界 移除祷告石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My understanding of your world is that to remove the prayer stones
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.85,0:50:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意味着与先知教堂决裂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is to break with the Seer Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.72,0:51:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.81,0:51:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 教会的教义是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is church doctrine, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.56,0:51:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我 他们仍在杀害 科学家和数学家吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me, are they still killing scientists and mathematicians?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.81,0:51:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你说的是大杀戮 那…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you're talking about the Purge, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.19,0:51:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教会用的词是“净化” 尊贵的大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The church's term is "the Cleanse," Your Exalteds.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.82,0:51:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据教会教义 是什么时候开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When was it, according to church doctrine,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.74,0:51:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习数学不再被视为异端分子 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that it stopped being heresy to study math?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.79,0:51:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今都是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It never stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.04,0:51:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你却解开了亚布拉克萨斯猜想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yet you solved the Abraxas Conjecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.29,0:51:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.38,0:51:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一个人们烧毁大学的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On a world where they burned the universities down.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.46,0:51:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里一定感到很孤独\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must have been lonely there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.09,0:51:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能想象到被哈里谢顿博士认可 是什么感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can imagine how it must have felt to be recognized by Dr. Hari Seldon.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.89,0:51:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有工作的机会 自我价值被认可\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To be given a job. To be valued.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.81,0:51:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.27,0:51:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道你是否能做到…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to know if there is any possible way…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.31,0:51:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哈里谢顿保持客观的态度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you can be objective about Hari Seldon.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.36,0:51:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 也许我做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know. Maybe I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.53,0:51:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许他带我来就是因为这个原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe that's why he brought me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.99,0:52:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚你有一个机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Last night you were given a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.66,0:52:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,评估谢顿博士的理论是否准确\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to assess the accuracy of Dr. Seldon's claims.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.95,0:52:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有结论了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you arrive at a conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.88,0:52:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.71,0:52:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.17,0:52:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢顿博士的预测…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dr. Seldon's calculations…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.59,0:52:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是正确的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.22,0:52:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国将灭亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Empire is dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.93,0:52:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.64,0:52:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}End this.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.87,0:52:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里 看天空\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hari, the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.49,0:52:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星桥那边不太对劲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something's wrong with the Star Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.19,0:53:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请心怀尊敬 享受和平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please respect and enjoy the peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.32,0:53:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返回母星时间 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Expected return to home planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.36,0:53:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.66,0:53:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-请心怀尊敬 享受和平 -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Please respect and enjoy the peace. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.46,0:53:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本车厢即将开始沿着轨道下降\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This car will commence its descent down the stalk momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.63,0:53:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您可能会有颠簸感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You may feel a jolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.84,0:53:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在开始下降前安坐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please secure yourself before commencing descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.71,0:57:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接川陀站的索道像绞刑具一样缠绕星球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The tether wrapped around the planet like a garrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.08,0:57:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵌入地表以下50层\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It cut 50 levels down.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.79,0:57:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-大帝 -闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Emperor-- -Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.43,0:57:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说在爆炸前有人听到安纳克里昂 和狄斯比斯的战吼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are reports of Anacreon and Thespin war cries before the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.56,0:57:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛之歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Songs of rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.69,0:57:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝对没有参与这件事 我们发…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We had no part in this, we--
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.02,0:57:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将退回你们的礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will, of course, be returning your gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.36,0:57:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,86963777\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}86,963,777.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.12,0:57:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,86963791\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}86,963,791.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.63,0:57:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这里做什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.93,0:57:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向委员会提出呈请\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I petitioned the committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.22,0:57:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说死了一亿人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're saying a hundred million dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.47,0:58:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外围星域可能反叛了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Outer Reaches may be in rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.35,0:58:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次袭击改变了一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The attack's changed everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.02,0:58:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里说你死去的概率非零\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hari said there's a nonzero chance you'll die,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.82,0:58:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但非零仍然是一个数字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but nonzero is still a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.49,0:58:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖尔 他们会杀死哈里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're gonna kill Hari, Gaal.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.33,0:58:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你不用与他一起死去 -我已经说了他的预测是正确的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You don't have to die with him. -I've already said his math was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.08,0:58:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你又检查了一次 说你弄错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Say you looked at it again. Say you were wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.00,0:58:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你失去信念了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've lost faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.17,0:58:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.67,0:58:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不需要那个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She doesn't need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.68,0:58:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.23,0:58:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先说还是你先说 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shall I speak first, or will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.23,0:58:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必客气 谢顿博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By all means, Dr. Seldon.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.40,0:58:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.49,0:58:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把一切归咎于我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You hold us responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.03,0:58:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How could I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.45,0:58:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的科学研究能够预测社会行为、趋势 无法预测个人行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My science can predict societal actions. Trends. Not individual ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.08,0:59:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但发生这件事我并不意外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'm not surprised it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.87,0:59:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.16,0:59:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们分身乏术了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're stretched too thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.33,0:59:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以外围星域的王国率先袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's why the kingdoms of the Outer Reach struck first.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.38,0:59:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁能怪他们呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And who can blame them?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.97,0:59:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感知到你们的脆弱后 很快将有其他力量 开始对帝国进行破坏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sensing vulnerability, soon other players will begin to apply downward pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.59,0:59:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河中某个主要的宗教必然会发起煽动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An exhortation from one of the galaxy's major religions is a given.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.77,0:59:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是川陀本地发起的起义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or perhaps a homegrown insurrection here on Trantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.23,0:59:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星桥的事 这是谁干的 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Star Bridge. Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.23,0:59:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.02,0:59:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我一个原因 说服我不该立即处决你和你的信众\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me why I shouldn't kill you and your followers right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.78,0:59:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的信众与此事无关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My followers aren't responsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.32,0:59:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你这么做 你一年内就会死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you do, you'll be dead within the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.37,0:59:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才开口了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The prodigy speaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.17,0:59:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.76,0:59:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手下杰瑞尔 让我检查谢顿博士的计算结果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your agent Jerril asked me to check Dr. Seldon's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.05,1:00:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对等式进行了进一步的计算\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I went a little farther in the equation.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.26,1:00:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你杀死他 帝国将加速灭亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you kill him, the fall accelerates.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.81,1:00:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个数据对你们还真有利啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's a convenient data point for your side.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.40,1:00:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有他能缩短黑暗时期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only he can shorten the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.32,1:00:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他就消灭了希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kill him, you kill hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.20,1:00:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没了希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kill hope…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.53,1:00:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就会杀了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.74,1:00:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are the odds?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.66,1:00:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅有的两个能拯救银河的人 都在这个房间里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only two people who can save the galaxy are in this room.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.13,1:00:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而其中一人是错的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And one of them is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.51,1:00:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I agree.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.89,1:00:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果灭亡的速度可以加快 那可以减慢吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the fall can be accelerated, can it not also be slowed?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.85,1:00:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 减慢几个世纪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. By a few centuries.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.23,1:00:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别对我们有所隐瞒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't keep us in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.69,1:00:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终止帝国克隆活动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}End imperial cloning.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.44,1:00:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国克隆终止了战乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Imperial cloning stopped the wars.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.20,1:01:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国克隆带来和平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Imperial cloning brought peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.66,1:01:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这一脉相承的王朝 已经统治了近四个世纪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our genetic dynasty has reigned for almost four centuries.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.20,1:01:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该很清楚 年轻的大脑拥有你的智慧 这件事的价值\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Surely you can understand the value in a younger mind who shares your intellect.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.96,1:01:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看见差异的价值\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I see the value in difference,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.13,1:01:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新想法的价值\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in the new.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.88,1:01:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有任何新的创造\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You offer nothing new.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.55,1:01:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是一个更嫩的葡萄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a younger grape…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.84,1:01:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自同一个葡萄藤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from the same vine,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.47,1:01:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注定酿成同样的酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}destined for the same old bottle.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.06,1:01:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们无法拯救自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't save yourselves…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.06,1:01:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你们能拯救功业 传承后世\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you can save your legacy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.19,1:01:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的功业还是我的功业 谢顿博士 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yours or mine, Dr. Seldon?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.63,1:01:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用了多久…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long did it take you…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.38,1:02:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激活元光体 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to trigger the Prime Radiant?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.97,1:02:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第二次尝试时成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got it on the second try.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.10,1:02:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早知道他们会交给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You knew they'd offer it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.31,1:02:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里 看着它时 我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hari, when I looked at it, I--
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.73,1:02:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的以为他们至少会假装一下 让整个过程看起来更公平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I really thought they'd try and make it seem more of a fair fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.78,1:02:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他们甚至连装都不愿装 对吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But they didn't bother, did they?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.74,1:02:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们尝试了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did we?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.41,1:02:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钩子那边还疼吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The hook still hurting you?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.62,1:02:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛拉斯用了你之前的话 “我很孤独”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Xylas used the same phrase you did. "I was lonely."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.00,1:02:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在窃听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They were listening.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.04,1:02:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他们在窃听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you knew they were listening.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.67,1:02:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他们正在窃听 -好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-They're listening now. -Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.34,1:02:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让他们听什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want them to hear?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.63,1:02:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚布拉克萨斯猜想是饵 你不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abraxas was the bait. Not you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.64,1:02:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在他们出手之前先行一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just moved before they did.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.27,1:02:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的话语权比你意识到的更大 盖尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have more agency here, Gaal, than you realize.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.87,1:03:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝决定 处决你们并非最佳选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Emperor has determined that your deaths are not the optimal outcome
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.13,1:03:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于帝国的福祉而言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the good of the Imperium.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.80,1:03:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝允许你们完善心理历史学研究\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will be allowed to refine your work on psychohistory,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.13,1:03:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建造你们的基地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to build your Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.64,1:03:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但地点不在川陀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But not on Trantor.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.31,1:03:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是端点星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Terminus.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.52,1:03:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座落于外缘区的无人之地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is uninhabited, sitting in the Periphery,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.85,1:03:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在银河外围星域的边上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}along the galaxy's Outer Reach.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.86,1:03:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安纳克里昂和狄斯比斯也位于外缘区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anacreon and Thespis are also in the Periphery.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.48,1:03:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 你们将与蛮族王国为邻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, the barbarian kingdoms will be your neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.74,1:03:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们将乘坐慢速舰旅行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will journey via slow ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.49,1:03:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国禁止你们使用跃迁技术\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Empire forbids you access to jumpdrive technology.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.62,1:03:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要流放我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're exiling us.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.29,1:03:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在端点星上 你们将不会为川陀制造麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On Terminus, you will not trouble Trantor,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.25,1:03:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国的和平将不受干扰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and there will be no disturbance of the Emperor's peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.13,1:04:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河众人将知道你们在阻止灭亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The galaxy will know that you are fighting the fall.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.59,1:04:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果心理历史学被证伪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If psychohistory proves fraudulent,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.22,1:04:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的基地将衰败和消失\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your Foundation will be allowed to wither and vanish.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.18,1:04:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if it's successful,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.93,1:04:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会将其合并 利用基地巩固你的政权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you'll co-opt it and use it to bolster your regime.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.94,1:04:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,端点星 我从没听过这个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Terminus. I've never even heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.19,1:04:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很合理 它在五万光年外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no reason you would. It's 50,000 light-years away.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.95,1:04:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有跃迁驱动器 去那里需要…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Without a jumpdrive, the journey there--
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.20,1:04:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-878天 -大约\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-878 days. -Approximately.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.00,1:04:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会有事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.75,1:04:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会遇到困难 这毫无疑问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There'll be hardships, no question.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.46,1:04:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,端点星围绕一颗红矮星转动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Terminus orbits a red dwarf.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.71,1:04:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的季节气候极端 金属和矿物稀缺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Its seasons are extreme. Metal and mineral poor.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.67,1:04:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know it well.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.76,1:04:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始的计划就是被流放\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Exile was always the plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.22,1:04:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,端点星一直是最优地点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Terminus was always the optimal location.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.97,1:04:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远在外缘区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out in the Periphery.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.64,1:04:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有帝国支持 不受帝国监控 完美地点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Imperial support without imperial eyes. It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.39,1:05:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有多少人知道 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many others knew?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.56,1:05:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有瑞驰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only Raych.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.94,1:05:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对大帝说的话…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What you said to the Emperor…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.99,1:05:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在检查我的计算结果时算到哪一步了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much farther into my math did you look?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.36,1:05:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底看到了什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you actually see?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.32,1:05:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我看不出来 -所以你说了假话 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I couldn't quite figure it. -So, you lied?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.37,1:05:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了一个假设\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hypothesized.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.95,1:05:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在辛纳克斯 没有人想知道海平面在上升\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On Synnax, no one wanted to hear that our seas were rising.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.21,1:05:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得如果能让人们听进去我的话 我就可能救下他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought if I could make people listen, that I could save them.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.63,1:05:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变是令人恐惧的 对于掌权者来说尤其如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Change is frightening, especially to those in power.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.76,1:05:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到大帝的恐惧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I could feel the Empire's fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.68,1:05:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我看进元光体时 我能看见黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I looked into the Prime Radiant, I could see the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.60,1:05:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一开始让我喘不过气来 难以承受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It took my breath away at first. It was crushing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.27,1:05:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我往更深的地方看去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But then I looked deeper,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.27,1:05:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看到尽头有一丝光亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I could see this tiny sliver of light at the very end of it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.36,1:05:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我意识到他们恐惧的不是灭亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I realized it's not the fall they're afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.87,1:05:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是你的计划可能会成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the chance that your plan will actually succeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.54,1:06:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建造比摧毁更需要力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It takes more power to build than to burn.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.00,1:06:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想建造 哈里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I want to build, Hari.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.92,1:06:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会有机会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll get your chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.09,1:06:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是基地的第一次危机 也不会是最后一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't the Foundation's first crisis, and it won't be our last.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.80,1:06:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有种感觉 你已经知道下一次危机是什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something tells me you already know what the next crisis will be.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.39,1:06:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝王的和平将会持续下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Emperor's peace will be maintained.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.11,1:06:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从辛纳克斯到川陀 现在向端点星进发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From Synnax to Trantor. Now Terminus.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.74,1:06:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这里是希望能拯救你的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You came here hoping to save your world.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.24,1:06:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请求你把梦想扩大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm asking you to dream bigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.74,1:06:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救一个世界太少了 何不拯救整个银河 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why stop at one world? Why not save the galaxy?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.79,1:06:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.22,1:06:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（端点星）
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.69,1:07:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（35年后）
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.40,1:07:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里计划了这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hari had planned for it all,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.61,1:07:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有他能预见的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}things only he saw over the horizon.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.12,1:07:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（基地）
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.62,1:07:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心理历史学能够预测整个人口的行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Psychohistory could forecast the behavior of entire populations
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.41,1:07:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精确度极高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with stunning accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.33,1:07:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是个人行为就难以预测了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, when it came to individuals, things got murkier.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.68,1:07:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人能接近穹窿 只有塞佛哈定是个例外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one could approach the Vault. No one but an outlier like Salvor Hardin.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.27,1:07:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I always wondered…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.60,1:07:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里在制定计划时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when Hari was formulating his plan,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.35,1:07:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是否意识到银河的命运 取决于她在里面所发现的东西 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}did he realize the galaxy's fate would rest on what she found inside?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.15,1:07:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为他知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think he did.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.99,1:07:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为那是他最怕的一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I think that's what he feared the most.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.68,1:08:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（纪念琳达安利维坦）
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.23,1:09:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字幕翻译：易晗